*{{tl|ISO 3166 code}} &ndash; (Code)
*{{tl|ISO 3166 code-3}} &ndash; (3 letter code)
*{{tl|ISO 3166 numeric}} &ndash; (numeric code)
*[[Module:ISO 3166/data]] &ndash; the data subpages used by this module

